GET http://localhost:3000/image?token=THE-TOKEN&memeId=SOME-IDENTIFIER

or specify query params:    token - THE-TOKEN
                            memeId - identifier of the requested meme
                            targetFileSize - optional parameter that specifies the requested file size of the rendered meme.
                                             The transmitted base64 encoding is about 37% larger, but the final image should be below this threshold.

Login required

No body.
